cs.CR, cs.MM, cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.CV 

The paper discusses techniques for improving the undetectability of network steganography methods, which involves both computer security (cs.CR) and multimedia (cs.MM) aspects. The techniques involve manipulating network traffic, which falls under the category of network infrastructure (cs.NI). The paper also discusses the use of machine learning (cs.IT) and image processing (cs.CV) techniques to improve steganogram extraction.
